7 An Act relating to public indebtedness; amending 62
O.S. 2021, Section 574, which relates to the Bond
8 Issue Proceeds Act; modifying expenditure of certain
allocated monies; amending Section 1, Chapter 157,
9 O.S.L. 2023 (70 O.S. Supp. 2024, Section 15-110),
