14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 62 O.S. 2021, Section 574, is
16 amended to read as follows:
17 Section 574. A. At any election upon the question of issuing
18 bonds, which if approved would require an ad valorem tax levy or
19 pledging the full faith and credit of the State of Oklahoma, the
20 governmental entity calling such election shall set forth in each
21 proposition to be voted upon the general purpose for which the bond
22 proceeds will be expended. This shall not require the proposition
23 or the bond to recite specific projects and dollar amounts.
